room_title: Escape room "Apartment 13" by The Chamber Escape Rooms in Fort Wayne
room_address: 3225 St Joe Center Rd, Fort Wayne, IN 46835
room_description: As you're walking by an apartment you hear a scream, and you're not quite sure what to make of it. You slowly open the door and walk in, and the next thing you know the apartment door slams shut behind you. You attempt to open it but it's jammed shut and you're trapped. How will you ​​escape this apartment with a twist?
